{
  "stem": "19518.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 90.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I just-- first of all, I was not strong enough to do any-- any damage to anybody, even if I wanted to.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I don't think that we can do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think that we were brought up that way to harm anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I guess that's why we didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't participate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That's why maybe we didn't insist on an immediate punishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Whatever punishment they had later on, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they went to prison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Whoever was round up went to prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This we know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a choice to make.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After-- yes, and the care was given to us too, medical care, via glucose injection to bring us back to life, to give us some more stamina.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The food was brought in five times a day, a little bit at a time, and not heavy stuff, so whoever was able to come back to themselves.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then sometimes in July-- we don't-- there was a treaty made with Russia that a certain part of Austria belonged to Russia, a certain part to whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Either go back to our country, or go to a DP camp in deep Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't savor either choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I felt maybe by pure, sheer luck, if I went through years of hardship, years of deprivation, typhoid, two typhoids at the same time, sick like a dog, frozen feet-- maybe by pure, sheer luck, one of my sisters survived.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I chose to go back to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Good or bad, or in between, we don't going to discuss that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] many survivors did go back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a mistake, maybe, I admit.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
